00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:30.840
sharp, but pressing straight down, at most
I’m going to get a fine hairline scratch,

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:37.800
like you would with a razor. If an opponent
has a knife in their palm, the back of the

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:41.771
hand will not open up. If I try and grab the
blade, and pull the knife anyway I’m going

00:00:41.771 --> 00:00:46.579
to be losing some fingers. If I keep the knife
from thrusting or drawing by grasping the

00:00:46.579 --> 00:00:51.160
wrist, and I push against the blade so the
handle is pushing against his fingers, even

00:00:51.160 --> 00:00:54.750
if it’s against a bigger attacker I can
free that knife. and Bring a straight stab

00:00:54.750 --> 00:01:00.261
