handle to strike the opponent or simply toss

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:36.820
the knife. One more time, I’ll show what
not to do. If he brings this at me and I simply

00:01:36.820 --> 00:01:40.050
grab the blade, I’m going to be bleeding
severely, because there is nothing to give

00:01:40.050 --> 00:01:46.560
